stories.title: 'Today wasn't a day for us' - Atapattu
stories.subTitle: India v Sri Lanka, 6th ODI, Rajkot
stories.summary: The win at Ahmedabad proved to be a momentary high for Marvan Atapattu and his men, who were at the receiving end of a mauling in the sixth game. A downcast Atapattu spoke to the press at the end of the game

stories.subTitle: India v Sri Lanka, 6th ODI, Rajkot
stories.summary: Rajkot, the capital of the erstwhile state of Saurashtra, may no longer retain its princely outlook but it doesn't take too long for cricket buffs to talk about its contribution to cricket
